item.title: CVE-2023-46659|2023-10-25T13:45:58.826Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20edgewall%20trac%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Edgewall Trac Plugin 1.13 and earlier does not escape the Trac website URL on the build page, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.
